the 100 dispatch,

01:00:40.270 --> 01:00:41.537
they're on their way.

01:00:41.538 --> 01:00:43.072
- They'll be right back, okay?

01:00:43.073 --> 01:00:45.608
Just in a few minutes and
I'm going to send for help.

01:00:45.609 --> 01:00:48.577
- No, don't go back out there.

01:00:48.578 --> 01:00:50.714
- He's my responsibility.

01:00:50.715 --> 01:00:52.015
- Helen.

01:01:08.598 --> 01:01:11.268
- You be a good mother.

01:01:12.469 --> 01:01:14.238
You have, fresh eyes.

01:01:35.093 --> 01:01:36.093
- Lucas?

01:02:19.603 --> 01:02:21.038
- Lucas.

01:02:23.040 --> 01:02:24.040
Lucas.

01:03:50.594 --> 01:03:51.928
- Lucas?

01:03:51.929 --> 01:03:52.996
- Helen?

01:04:33.337 --> 01:04:34.537
- Lucas?

01:07:19.870 --> 01:07:20.870
Lucas?

01:07:39.857 --> 01:07:40.857
Lucas.

01:07:43.893 --> 01:07:47.296
- Shh, quiet,
or he'll come back.

01:07:47.297 --> 01:07:48.997
- Come on, let's go.

01:08:42.687 --> 01:08:43.687
- Helen.

01:08:43.688 --> 01:08:44.754
- Casey.

01:08:48.558 --> 01:08:51.194
All the stories are
true, they never stop.

01:09:08.645 --> 01:09:09.845
- Hey.

01:09:09.845 --> 01:09:12.046
- No, Lucas stop, Lucas run.

01:09:29.399 --> 01:09:31.300
- Lucas, get out of the way.

01:09:38.107 --> 01:09:39.108
Move, Lucas.

01:10:22.286 --> 01:10:23.786
- Okay.

01:10:23.787 --> 01:10:24.821
You go that way.

01:10:33.597 --> 01:10:35.531
- Hey, Bowery, I'm right here,

01:10:35.532 --> 01:10:36.632
come and get me.

01:10:48.278 --> 01:10:49.678
Come and get me.

01:10:49.679 --> 01:10:52.147
Come on, I'm here,
come and get me.

01:11:02.393 --> 01:11:03.393
- Helen!

01:11:15.171 --> 01:11:16.905
- Lucas.

01:11:16.906 --> 01:11:18.206
- Wait, no.

01:11:23.713 --> 01:11:24.713
- No!

01:11:28.518 --> 01:11:29.553
No!

01:12:35.752 --> 01:12:37.185
- You're dead.

01:12:44.227 --> 01:12:45.561
You want it?

